        "section_sub": "",
        "description": "<p>We're thrilled to announce our collaboration with MOVE this summer, a portuguese NGO dedicated to empowering micro-entrepreneurs in underdeveloped regions including Azores, São Tomé e Príncipe, Timor Leste. At Paez, we believe in the power of fostering younger generations to create positive change, and this collaboration allows us to start tapping our feet to do so.</p>",
